theLoadBalancerName The name associated with the LoadBalancer. The name must be unique within the client AWS account.
theAvailabilityZones A list of Availability Zones to be removed from the LoadBalancer. <note> There must be at least one Availability Zone registered with a LoadBalancer at all times. The client cannot remove all the Availability Zones from a LoadBalancer. Specified Availability Zones must be in the same Region. </note>
